<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Account Activation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #4a6fa5;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #4a6fa5;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .warning {
            color: #d9534f;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>You were invited to project {{projectName}} in {{appName}}, dear user!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>To accept the invite, please press the button below:</p>
        
        <a href="{{invitationLink}}" class="button">Accept invite</a>
        
        <p>If the button doesn't work, please copy and paste the following link into your browser:</p>
        <p><small>{{invitationLink}}</small></p>

        <p class="warning">⚠️ This link will be expired on {{expiresAt}}.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This email was sent automatically. Please do not reply.</p>
        <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} {{appName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>